{"id":251239,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-安徽女访民冯友苗上访被拘留，释放后仍/","date":"2012-09-12T05:01:04Z","modified":"2012-09-12T05:01:04Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽女访民冯友苗上访被拘留，释放后仍不放弃维权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽省安庆市女访民冯友苗因</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月，住房被非法拆除后未获补偿，几年赴区、市和省政府上访无果，无奈之下于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年赴京上访，今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月到天安门广场撒上访材料，被北京警方训诫后送久敬庄关押，被安庆市政府驻京办接出后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>被安庆市警方以“传唤”名义押回安庆后被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在拘留期间，冯友苗曾绝食两天抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日上午</span><span>，获释后的冯友苗再次到安徽省政府上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据冯友苗反映，她是因唯一的住房被非法拆除，其后政府推诿要她去找安庆石化，她多次遭遇威胁，为了获安置补偿，经三年上访，如今政府愿意支付的补偿费是按三年前的数额，而这几年房价飞涨，，三年前的数额在今天岂能购置到三年前同样面积地段的房子，故其绝不同意，而这三年的安置过渡费也未给付，如今冯友苗一家只得在外租房居住，她期待安徽省政府信访局能够查明案情，使她能够获得公正的补偿安置，以保障其财产权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-J9k-6mDlqEQ/UE_vm6pcFEI/AAAAAAAAOA0/yl5haN73ZfY/s1600/P1020685.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-J9k-6mDlqEQ/UE_vm6pcFEI/AAAAAAAAOA0/yl5haN73ZfY/s320/P1020685.JPG\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-0ZWZ6EDzdtU/UE_vpFxcopI/AAAAAAAAOA8/LeA0K48PUgQ/s1600/P1020686.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-0ZWZ6EDzdtU/UE_vpFxcopI/AAAAAAAAOA8/LeA0K48PUgQ/s320/P1020686.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RULOeHJ0eq4/UE_vrnBX39I/AAAAAAAAOBE/PFjpex6Nq0E/s1600/P1020687.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RULOeHJ0eq4/UE_vrnBX39I/AAAAAAAAOBE/PFjpex6Nq0E/s320/P1020687.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5073180783063287173?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}